{"tid":2378424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說有個傻仔貪平去咗速剪","createTime":"2021-01-24T12:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T08:13:42.000Z","uid":371366,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"378793402515e69f168789251f5d18e363d055cd","tid":2378424,"uid":371366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"冇錯嗰個就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，今日去剪頭髮，同個髮型師講側面剷小小留返under cut , 點知佢剷個陣勁大力， 好似想鋤甩我個頭，大大力咁撞埋來。<br />\n<br />\n之後又係啲經典慘劇啦， 話前陰剪少少，就剪咗一大忽，又鳩噏一大堆話幫我剪啲層次，頂你個肺,個頭煲蓋咁有閪層次咩。<br />\n<br />\n最後剪完，正常髮型師應該攞鏡照下後邊，佢野都冇講就咁行咗出舖頭，屌都屌唔切。所以奉勸大家想平剪頭髮都係去返QB house , 如果唔係就會變咗敍俊，我都知自己柒，揀啲平價速剪， 但係都唔係咁唔尊重客人掛... ... 一個月後又一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f946801139c1234746727a6073575b9fcb6031e","tid":2378424,"uid":151264,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:44:38.000Z","msg":"人柒剪咩都柒"},{"pid":"a44c6227a96867034cf9dad3984aec11843b467f","tid":2378424,"uid":323414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"其實冇想像中咁差喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2062a7441fa1d2eeeccc597d734cb934c01ebd","tid":2378424,"uid":221016,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"樓豬係lunch 哥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1022435e44ef0daa63ee563cd9751680f401d5f8","tid":2378424,"uid":311566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"笑撚到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個龜頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實都唔差吖"},{"pid":"64a79a0ab98623cc13bb1bdaa60a764